        <span class='text-zinc-500'>2020</span>
        <span class='ml-2 mr-2'>—</span>
        <a href='https://github.com/MorkWood2/save-team'>Save Team!</a>
        <p class='text-zinc-500'>
          <span class='ml-1 mr-1'>:</span> React site that raises awareness
          about a program I benefited from in High School
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class='flex items-center'>
        <span class='text-zinc-500'>2019</span>
        <span class='ml-2 mr-2'>—</span>
        <a href='https://github.com/MorkWood2/neo-art'>Art_Project_2</a>
        <p class='text-zinc-500'>
          <span class='ml-1 mr-1'>:</span> Public art project
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class='flex items-center'>
        <span class='text-zinc-500'>2019</span>
        <span class='ml-2 mr-2'>—</span>
        <a href='https://github.com/MorkWood2/React-github-search'
          >Github User Search</a
        >
        <p class='text-zinc-500'>
          <span class='ml-1 mr-1'>:</span> React Github user search app
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class='flex items-center'>
        <span class='text-zinc-500'>2019</span>
        <span class='ml-2 mr-2'>—</span>
        <a href='https://github.com/MorkWood2/people-finder'>People Finder</a>
        <p class='text-zinc-500'>
          <span class='ml-1 mr-1'>:</span> Full stack MERN React app using react
          hooks, context, JWT authentication
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class='flex items-center'>
        <span class='text-zinc-500'>2018</span>
        <span class='ml-2 mr-2'>—</span>
        <a href='https://morkwood2.github.io/Public_Art_Map/'>Public Art Map</a>
        <p class='text-zinc-500'>
